Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:50.01,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFE100&\3a&HFF&\pos(408,984)}心澄如镜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:50.01,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(680,1017.667)} -> 正是所求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.01,0:01:52.22,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}因为想要守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:54.84,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}所以向着你呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:59.81,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}暗中宣战 献身歃血 以证逆命
